00:29:40.620 --> 00:29:43.460
Tela floral barata.

00:29:43.460 --> 00:29:44.580
Tejido floral.

00:29:45.500 --> 00:29:47.220
Señor, tomaré uno.

00:29:47.460 --> 00:29:48.660
- Cosas de buena calidad. - Tómalo con calma.

00:29:48.660 --> 00:29:49.660
Tome su tiempo.

00:29:50.700 --> 00:29:53.380
